  "title": "Aviation Service Engine Technician",
  "description": "<p>With its latest and newest expanded facilities and constantly developing new capabilities for both its engine overhaul and component repair businesses in Singapore, our client will be investing millions for the next phase of Expansion Plan.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are inviting passionate applicants to join the company as Aircraft Engine Technicians and to take the next flight together in your Career Growth!!</p>\n<h2><strong>✨ Job Highlights:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>🚐 <strong>Islandwide Door-to-Door Transport Provided</strong></li>\n  <li>💰 <strong>Attractive Variable Bonus – Up to 4 Months!</strong></li>\n  <li>🎁 <strong>13th Month Annual Wage Supplement (AWS)</strong></li>\n  <li>⏱️ <strong>Guaranteed Overtime Pay</strong></li>\n  <li>💼 <strong>Annual Flexi-Benefits of $1,700</strong></li>\n  <li>🌙 <strong>Shift Allowances</strong></li>\n  <li>📈 <strong>Stable Career Growth and Development</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>🔧 Job Summary:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Job Type:</strong> Full-Time, Shift Work</li>\n  <li><strong>Working Hours:<br>\n</strong>Morning Shift: 6:30 AM – 4:15 PM<br>\nAfternoon Shift: 4:00 PM – 1:45 AM</li>\n  <li><strong>Shift Pattern:</strong> 4 Days On / 2 Days Off</li>\n  <li><strong>Location:</strong> Changi (Company transport provided islandwide)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2><strong>🔩 Responsibilities:</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform inspection, repair, and replacement of damaged or worn-out aircraft engine parts.</li>\n  <li>Use technical manuals and specialized tools to ensure all work meets safety and quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Follow maintenance schedules and standard operating procedures.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with engineering and quality teams to ensure compliance with regulatory standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>Chong Wei Lian (William) | Registration Number: R23115965<br>\nAlwaysHired Pte Ltd | EA Licence No: 24C2293</p>",
